snippet.title: Marvel Rivals: Get Ready for Launch! | Dev Vision Vol. 01
snippet.description:
In our first Marvel Rivals: Dev Vision, our Creative Director, Guangguang, shares details about our Seasonal Roadmap, Monetization, Servers, and much more as we approach our official launch on December 6th.

Our inaugural season, Dooms' Rise, will feature all-new content for an incredible one month experience at launch!

Watch the video below for more details and stay tuned to our socials for exciting updates as we approach launch day!

Are you excited to Ignite the Battle?

Play free now on: 
🔹 Steam: https://t.co/IPhy0Of1cG
🔹 PlayStation: https://t.co/FR0aVfTmcn
🔹 Xbox: https://t.co/GaAYz7Nku6
🔹 Epic Games: https://t.co/QXoxz0VAP7

Follow #MarvelRivals for the latest news:
🔹 Discord:https://discord.gg/marvelrivals
🔹 Twitter:https://twitter.com/MarvelRivals
🔹 Instagram:https://www.instagram.com/marvelrivals/
🔹 Facebook:https://www.facebook.com/marvelrivals/

🔹 Twitch:https://www.twitch.tv/marvelrivals
